      "role": "user",
      "content": "it actually feels impossible to even think about the future anymore. like, i look at the news and the climate data and i just feel this massive weight in my chest. everything is just breaking and there is no point in trying to build a life or a career or anything when the planet is literally dying. it feels like we're all just waiting for the end. how are you even supposed to find a reason to care about anything?",
